{"type":"message","id":"a2804697","parentId":"6f16d6c8","timestamp":"2026-03-16T23:37:20.525Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Checking daily report status**\n\nI need to find out if the user is asking about checking the baseline status in their workspace. It makes sense to read recent memory and see if any relevant skills apply, but it seems I don’t have that skill. Maybe I should inspect files related to 日报 or check git for any updates. Alright, I’ll search through the workspace for the necessary information. Let’s see what I can find!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yPomqkbhSGcp4U6ThFDZo0D1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pwd && echo '---' && find . -maxdepth 3 \\( -iname '*日报*' -o -iname '*daily*' -o -iname '*report*' -o -iname '*baseline*' -o -iname '*基线*' \\) | sed 's#^./##' | sort","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":270,"output":192,"cacheRead":32256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32718,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773704230871}}
