{"type":"message","id":"28a87c3f","parentId":"3e880770","timestamp":"2026-03-17T02:01:50.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Summarizing changes and next steps**\n\nI see that we've changed credentials and disabled the group. Now I need to summarize this and mention the next candidate for approval. Since we've already approved the state change, I should note that the user requested tighter permissions. Although we could go further, we didn't succeed in that part. It’s better to mention what we've accomplished and propose the next minimal set, especially since the sandbox change has been deferred due to risk. I'll keep it concise!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 先收紧了两项已经落地的：\n\n- **已禁用 Feishu 群聊**：`channels.feishu.groupPolicy = disabled`\n- **已收紧凭证目录权限**：`/root/.openclaw/credentials -> 700`\n\n这两项都是低副作用、收益很直接的。\n\n### 还没动的\n我本来准备继续补：\n- `gateway.auth.rateLimit`\n- sandbox 相关项\n\n但我在配置写入这一步停住了：  \n**配置接口要求带当前配置的基线哈希做安全写入**，我不想在没确认基线的情况下硬覆盖，避免把现有配置踩坏。\n\n### 接下来我建议的顺序\n1. **先补认证限流**  \n   风险低，收益高，不太影响正常使用。\n2. **再看 sandbox / workspace 边界**  \n   这块一旦收太猛，可能影响你当前主代理的使用体验，所以要谨慎。\n\n如果你要，我下一步就继续只做 **第 1 步：补 `gateway.auth.rateLimit`**，不碰 sandbox。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":227,"output":759,"cacheRead":45568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46554,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773712889764}}
