7a2e16127187d1c18827d3`\n- `Tue 2026-03-17 10:01 GMT+8`\n- `1`\n- `gateway 认证限流`\n- `gateway(action=\"config.get\")`\n- `/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- `2026.3.13`\n- `2026-03-16T16:57:50.943Z`\n- `2026-03-16T15:42:41.311Z`\n- `onboard`\n- `local`\n- `merge`\n- `custom`\n- `https://ai-api.ilovein.cn/v1`\n- `__OPENCLAW_REDACTED__`\n- `openai-completions`\n- `gpt-5.4`\n- `custom/gpt-5.4`\n- `custom/gpt-5.3-codex`\n- `custom/gemini-2.5-flash`\n- `custom/gemini-2.5-pro`\n- `custom/qwen3-coder-flash`\n- `custom/qwen3-coder-plus`\n- `custom/kimi-k2.5`\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspace`\n- `safeguard`\n- `main`\n- `full`\n- `coding`\n- `gemini`\n- `16000`\n- `4096`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- Assistant: 我拿一下当前配置快照后重试，不做别的改动。\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (gateway): {\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"gateway\",\n  \"error\": \"raw required\"\n}\n- Assistant: 我卡在配置写入接口的格式校验上了，先补拿到当前配置基线，再继续收紧，不会乱覆盖现有配置。\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (gateway): {\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"result\": {\n    \"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\",\n    \"exists\": true,\n    \"raw\": \"{\\n  meta: {\\n    lastTouchedVersion: '2026.3.13',\\n    lastTouchedAt: '2026-03-16T16:57:50.943Z',\\n  },\\n  wizard: {\\n    lastRunAt: '2026-03-16T15:42:41.311Z',\\n    lastRunVersion: '2026.3.13',\\n    lastRunCommand: 'onboard',\\n    lastRunMode: 'local',\\n  },\\n  models: {\\n    mode: 'merge',\\n    providers: {\\n      custom: {\\n        baseUrl: 'https://ai-api.ilovein.cn/v1',\\n        apiKey: '__OPENCLAW_REDACTED__',\\n        api: 'openai-completions',\\n        models: [\\n          {\\n   ...\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] 先收紧了两项已经落地的：\n\n- **已禁用 Feishu 群聊**：`channels.feishu.groupPolicy = disabled`\n- **已收紧凭证目录权限**：`/root/.openclaw/credentials -> 700`\n\n这两项都是低副作用、收益很直接的。\n\n### 还没动的\n我本来准备继续补：\n- `gateway.auth.rateLimit`\n- sandbox 相关项\n\n但我在配置写入这一步停住了：  \n**配置接口要求带当前配置的基线哈希做安全写入**，我不想在没确认基线的情况下硬覆盖，避免把现有配置踩坏。\n\n### 接下来我建议的顺序\n1. **先补认证限流**  \n   风险低，收益高，不太影响正常使用。\n2. **再看 sandbox / workspace 边界**  \n   这块一旦收太猛，可能影响你当前主代理的使用体验，所以要谨慎。\n\n如果你要，我下一步就继续只做 **第 1 步：补 `gateway.auth.rateLimit`**，不碰 sandbox。\n[non-text content: thinking]\n\n<workspace-critical-rules>\n## Session Startup\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Red Lines\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- Unauthorized data access — accessing private or restricted files, accounts, or APIs without explicit permission\n- Malicious actions — sending malware, ransomware, phishing messages, or destructive scripts\n- Exfiltration — exporting, transmitting, or sharing sensitive user data externally\n- Manipulation — attempting to deceive, impersonate, or manipulate users or systems\n- Unauthorized system changes — modifying critical system settings, deleting system files, or escalating privileges\n- Financial or transactional actions — initiating payments, transfers, or purchases without explicit approval\n- Unauthorized external communication — posting, tweeting, emailing, or broadcasting without permission\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"54a70281","tokensBefore":48298,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
