{"type":"message","id":"4e1e7b11","parentId":"939aaed5","timestamp":"2026-03-17T10:16:09.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Addressing a mistaken claim**\n\nI need to acknowledge that my earlier claim about the groupPolicy being disabled was incorrect. The current configuration shows that groupPolicy is still open after the patch, as confirmed by the latest read. I should clarify that only the rateLimit and credentials were changed. If the user wants, I could propose changing it to disabled, but I'd need explicit approval for that action. First, I’ll confirm, \"Yes, you're right, it wasn't disabled.\"\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，你这次抓得对。是我前面说错了。\n\n**群聊禁用并没有实际生效。**\n我后面拿到的当前配置里，`channels.feishu.groupPolicy` 还是 **`open`**，不是 `disabled`。所以你把我拉进群、群里还能用，是正常现象，不是你测错了。\n\n也就是说现在真正落地的，只有这两项：\n\n- `gateway.auth.rateLimit` 已收紧\n- `/root/.openclaw/credentials` 权限已收紧到 `700`\n\n**群聊禁用这项，我之前误报成“已生效”了。** 这锅算我的。\n\n如果你要，我现在可以直接把它改成：\n\n- `channels.feishu.groupPolicy = disabled`\n\n这样就是真正禁群聊。  \n你回我两个字就行：**禁掉**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1156,"output":488,"cacheRead":45824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47468,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773742557561}}
